# Internal working docs — kept locally, not tracked in the public repo.
# Pulled out 2026-04-22 pending explicit approvals to publish.
DECISIONS_LOG.md
PHASE1_PLAN.md

# Third-party proprietary data — kept locally, never committed.
# REDACTED compilations (member-only); CME feeder-futures are proprietary.
# The public repo sources Clovis data directly from USDA-AMS (public-domain)
# and treats CME futures as link-out only. See LICENSE-DATA.md.
Data_REDACTED/

# Local MARS API samples and scratch JSON. USDA-AMS data is public-domain
# and redistributable, but raw one-off pulls belong in data/raw/clovis/
# (also gitignored) under the pipeline's control; the top-level folder is
# a research scratchpad and we don't want 60+ MB blobs in the repo.
Data_USDA_AMS/

# Internal planning docs (Phase-0 Decision 7 — kept local until promotion)
PLAN_*.md

# Sandbox-only CSV artifacts (canonical historical block is .parquet via pyarrow)
data/processed/*.csv
